                            <comment id="17347838" author="edimitrova" created="Wed, 19 May 2021 19:31:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;First observations - this test fails only when &#160;the whole class is run. Running on its own it succeeds 500 runs. Also, the original python DTest looks good in Jenkins.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am wondering whether it is not in-jvm issue. This reminds me of&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
